trans-unit.source: Provides design-time visual support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"></xref> controls.

The WebZoneDesigner class is the abstract base class for both <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner>, which all the other zone designers inherit from.
trans-unit.target: WebZoneDesigner klassen är abstrakt basklass för både <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner>och <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner>, som alla andra zonen-designers som ärver från.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ToolZoneDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBaseDesigner>

trans-unit.source: By inheriting directly from <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> instead of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>, it allows implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method that do not automatically clear the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> collection, thus enabling the designer to render exceptions from child controls.
trans-unit.target: Genom att ärva direkt från <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>i stället för <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>, tillåter implementeringar av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden inte ta bort automatiskt i <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A>samling, vilket gör det möjligt att göra undantag från underordnade kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Like other designers in this namespace, WebZoneDesigner overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: Precis som andra användare i det här namnområdet WebZoneDesigner åsidosätter den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>egenskapen returnerar alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebZoneDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the designer bound to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en instans av designer bundna till den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone"></xref> control associated with the designer.
Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om designern ska använda en tillfällig kopia i stället för verkliga kontrollen som är associerade med designern för att generera designläge markering.
